DROP VIEW IF EXISTS custaggrview;
GO

CREATE VIEW custaggrview AS
SELECT * 
FROM  OPENROWSET(
        BULK 'https://synpasedlstore.dfs.core.windows.net/root/tpchoutput2/**',
        FORMAT = 'PARQUET'
    ) 
WITH
(
    [month] INT,
    [day] INT ,
    [O_ORDERDATE] DATE,
    [C_CUSTKEY] varchar(100),
    [Tprice] DECIMAL(10,2),
    [Tdicount] DECIMAL(10,2),
    [Tqty] DECIMAL(14, 2),
    [Ttax] DECIMAL(10,2),
    [Titem] INT,
    [Textprice] DECIMAL(19, 2)

) AS [r];


select top 10 * from custaggrview;
